      "para_id": "Q001531.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) To ..., her lady , Ninala , child of Ur-Bau , ruler of Lagaš , dedicated this ( female statuette ) for the well-being of Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , her spouse , and for her own well-being . The name of this statue is \" My lady called me , ( and ) I built it on the appointed day .\""
    }
  ],
